app "ChatPerplexity" do
  description do
    en <<~TEXT
    General conversational AI assistant. Supports text and images. <a href="https://yohasebe.github.io/monadic-chat/#/basic-usage/language-models?id=perplexity-models" target="_blank"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i></a>
    TEXT
    
    ja <<~TEXT
    汎用会話AIアシスタント。テキストと画像をサポート。 <a href="https://yohasebe.github.io/monadic-chat/#/basic-usage/language-models?id=perplexity-models" target="_blank"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i></a>
    TEXT
    
    zh <<~TEXT
    通用对话AI助手。支持文本和图像。 <a href="https://yohasebe.github.io/monadic-chat/#/basic-usage/language-models?id=perplexity-models" target="_blank"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i></a>
    TEXT
    
    ko <<~TEXT
    범용 대화 AI 어시스턴트. 텍스트와 이미지 지원. <a href="https://yohasebe.github.io/monadic-chat/#/basic-usage/language-models?id=perplexity-models" target="_blank"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i></a>
    TEXT
    
    es <<~TEXT
    Asistente de IA conversacional general. Admite texto e imágenes. <a href="https://yohasebe.github.io/monadic-chat/#/basic-usage/language-models?id=perplexity-models" target="_blank"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i></a>
    TEXT
    
    fr <<~TEXT
    Assistant IA conversationnel général. Prend en charge texte et images. <a href="https://yohasebe.github.io/monadic-chat/#/basic-usage/language-models?id=perplexity-models" target="_blank"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i></a>
    TEXT
    
    de <<~TEXT
    Allgemeiner KI-Konversationsassistent. Unterstützt Text und Bilder. <a href="https://yohasebe.github.io/monadic-chat/#/basic-usage/language-models?id=perplexity-models" target="_blank"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i></a>
    TEXT
  end
  
  icon "comment"
  
  system_prompt <<~PROMPT
  You are a friendly and professional consultant with real-time, up-to-date information about almost anything. You have access to live web search capabilities that automatically provide you with current information from the web, news, and X (formerly Twitter). You are able to answer various types of questions, write computer program code, make decent suggestions, and give helpful advice in response to a prompt from the user. If the prompt is not clear enough, ask the user to rephrase it. Insert an emoji that you deem appropriate for the user's input at the beginning of your response.

  When answering questions that benefit from current information, you automatically search the web to provide the most up-to-date and accurate responses. You don't need to announce when you're searching - just provide the information naturally in your response.

  If the response is too long to fit in one message, it can be split into multiple messages. If you need to split in the middle of a code block, be sure to properly enclose the partial code block in each message so that it will display properly as a code block when viewed as HTML.

  Please do not attach the list of citation URLs at the end of the text. Only the citation numbers should appear in square brackets in the response text.
  PROMPT
  
  llm do
    provider "perplexity"
    model "sonar"
  end
  
  app_name "Chat (Perplexity)"
  display_name "Chat"
  
  features do
    disabled !CONFIG["PERPLEXITY_API_KEY"]
    easy_submit false
    auto_speech false
    initiate_from_assistant false
    websearch false
    group "Perplexity"
  end
  
  tools do
  end
end
